Class FileAreaAdminUpdateDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.objects.FileAreaAdminUpdateDetails
All Implemented Interfaces:
DimensionsObjectDetails
Direct Known Subclasses:
DeploymentAreaAdminUpdateDetails, WorkAreaAdminUpdateDetails
public abstract class FileAreaAdminUpdateDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements DimensionsObjectDetails

Mutable abstract representation of the common update-able administrative properties of all File Area types. Keeps track of which properties have been set.
